         SCHOOL THEME — Centralized color config
         ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
         These are COMPILE-TIME defaults (GoIbibo-inspired warm orange).
         At RUNTIME, SchoolTheme.kt overrides them per school branding.
         To change the default look everywhere: edit only this file.
         ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

